{"type": "article", "id": 1052, "title": "乐高新系列复制 Banksy 涂鸦", "description": "由摄影师 Jeff Friesen 设计的乐高全新​ The Brick Fantastic 系列，把英国涂鸦大师 Banksy 的诸多经典作品用乐高积木重新演绎，增添了新的场景或者元素，让那些具有讽刺意味的画面统统萌了起来。", "date": "2014-06-06T11:53:05Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [{"id": 929, "name": "乐高"}, {"id": 138, "name": "Banksy"}, {"id": 139, "name": "涂鸦"}, {"id": 289, "name": "玩具"}], "category": 5, "column": null, "author": 6, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 3, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160604230130FxM01ui2PGaOwZWq.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t由摄影师 Jeff Friesen 设计的乐高全新<a href=\"http://www.thebrickfantastic.com/\" target=\"_blank\"> The Brick Fantastic</a> 系列，把英国街头艺术家 <a href=\"http://banksy.co.uk\" target=\"_blank\">Banksy</a> 的诸多经典涂鸦作品用乐高积木重新演绎，增添了新的场景或者元素，让那些具有讽刺意味的画面统统萌了起来。每张图片的角落你都可以看到 Banksy 的原作。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606042301255w7hXQd8H6yWozi3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604230126iCUfY5X8vxyrn7eE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.796875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604230126gtowU2RnsOBQ9Yi6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7984375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604230127cDWNEe1ozb94mOjq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7953125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606042301270BoSH2zZuxcQI6sE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.796875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604230128xg4C5phIPaKiDqLv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7984375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604230128JAyEedFxnIbUHTSa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7953125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604230129xPJ6wYCON32dU1H5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7984375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606042301297ojNEzGW2J8fAs1e.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.796875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604230130MoPFNcnyJk2Sg8Xp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.thebrickfantastic.com/new-gallery-bricksy-lego-banksy/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>欣赏更多作品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t题图来自<a href=\"http://www.thebrickfantastic.com/new-gallery-bricksy-lego-banksy/\" target=\"_blank\">thebrickfantastic</a>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}